Milx (a.k.a. C++ on Rails) aims to be a C++ web development framework, based
on Rails and Cake PHP structure.

Milx is a pure academic framework (at least now), and doesn't aims to be a
production framework.

Project Leader:
Carlos Júnior <carlos@milk-it.net>

Contributors:
